sparqlQuery:
PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>
PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
SELECT DISTINCT ?uri 
WHERE {
	?uri rdf:type dbo:City .
        ?uri dbo:isPartOf res:New_Jersey .
        ?uri dbp:populationTotal ?inhabitants .
        FILTER (?inhabitants > 100000) .
}

languageToQuestion.en: Give me all cities in New Jersey with more than 100000 inhabitants.
languageToQuestion.pt_BR: Liste todas as cidades em New Jersey com mais de 100000 habitantes.
languageToQuestion.de: Gib mir alle Städte in New Jersey, die mehr als 100000 Einwohner haben.
languageToQuestion.es: Dame todas las cuidades en New Jersey que tengan más de 100000 habitantes.
languageToQuestion.it: Dammi tutte le città del New Jersey con più di 100000 abitanti.
languageToQuestion.fr: Donnes-moi toutes les villes du New Jersey avec plus de 100000 habitants.
languageToQuestion.nl: Geef alle steden in New Jersey met meer dan 100000 inwoners.
languageToQuestion.hi_IN: मुझे न्यू जर्सी के १००००० से अधिक निवासियों के साथ सभी शहरों की सूचि बतायें।
